text: The District of La Vallée was a district in the canton of Vaud. The seat of the district was the municipality of Le Chenit. It is now part of the Jura- Nord vaudois District. * Cercle du Chenit ** Le Chenit * Cercle du Pont ** L'Abbaye ** Le Lieu Category:Former districts of Vaud
title: La Vallée (district)
